# iOS & iPadOS 16.3 Release Notes

**Article**

Update your apps to use new features, and test your apps against API changes.

## Overview

The iOS & iPadOS 16.2 SDK provides support to develop apps for iPhone and iPad running iOS & iPadOS 16.3. The SDK comes bundled with Xcode 14.2, available from the Mac App Store. For information on the compatibility requirements for Xcode 14.2, see [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Xcode-Release-Notes/xcode-14_2-release-notes].

### General

There are no new release notes for this software update.
